    "description": "《佣兵传奇１》是一款回合制战棋RPG。<br>本作是该系列的第一款作品，随后还有多部内容充实的续作。例如该系列的最新成员《佣兵烈焰》和《佣兵重生》。<br><br>[游戏特点]<br>・斜45度视角的像素风战场——指挥你的角色，带领他们走向胜利！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/b72aea932bfa1919c4e4fdd840c2eef7.poster.avif?t=1727198673\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/b72aea932bfa1919c4e4fdd840c2eef7.webm?t=1727198673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/b72aea932bfa1919c4e4fdd840c2eef7.mp4?t=1727198673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>・SP转职系统——角色升级之后，可以转为高级和专家职业，从而学习新的技能。<br>有些物品可以解锁特殊职业。根据您的喜好组建一支菁英队伍吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/bdd6ade8adf767ab1ea5dc4f1fa3be10.poster.avif?t=1727198673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/bdd6ade8adf767ab1ea5dc4f1fa3be10.webm?t=1727198673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/bdd6ade8adf767ab1ea5dc4f1fa3be10.mp4?t=1727198673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・SP学习技能——学习并利用各种技能来对敌人施加增益、减益或疾病状态。<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/b63a7f1a9d3d9eb48358cc4f80fc0c01.poster.avif?t=1727198673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/b63a7f1a9d3d9eb48358cc4f80fc0c01.webm?t=1727198673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/b63a7f1a9d3d9eb48358cc4f80fc0c01.mp4?t=1727198673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/eaff9dc69ed28bc1a4aa94ed9312bbbb.poster.avif?t=1727198673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/eaff9dc69ed28bc1a4aa94ed9312bbbb.webm?t=1727198673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142230/extras/eaff9dc69ed28bc1a4aa94ed9312bbbb.mp4?t=1727198673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>・多结局故事线——您的选择会影响每个角色的命运。<br><br>・Ex关卡——为高手玩家提供额外的挑战性关卡。<br><br><br>[故事]<br>绿色大陆福尔尼亚以其广阔的土地和温暖的气候而闻名。<br>位于大陆西南一带的弗雷尔王国，近年来不断入侵其邻国。<br>由于担心弗雷尔王国的势力不断增强，大陆南端的蒙多阿王国入侵了小国塞克拉克，以占领更多的领土。<br>蒙多阿遭到了对手的激烈抵抗。随着战事的延长，这种情况给为金钱而战的佣兵们带来了极大的利益。许多大型佣兵团利用这个机会，往口袋里塞了满满的黄金。<br>但对于那些尚未建立名声的人来说，情况则有所不同。<br>本作讲述了许多不同的故事，聚焦于年轻的指挥官莱昂和他仅有六名新手佣兵的部队：白狮佣兵团……",
